io.spine.client

Class ColumnFilters

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.client.ColumnFilters

  • public final class ColumnFilters
extends java.lang.Object
    A factory of ColumnFilter instances.

    The public methods of this class represent the recommended way to create a ColumnFilter.

    Comparision types

    The Column filters support two generic kinds of comparison:

    1. Equality comparison;
    2. Ordering comparison.

    The equality comparison supports any data type for the Entity Columns.

    The ordering comparison (>, <, >=, <=) support only following data types for the Entity Columns:

    • com.google.protobuf.Timestamp;
    • Java primitive number types;
    • String.
    See Also:
    for the application
